---

---

<section id="about" class="section-container">
  <h2 class="section-title reveal">
    About <span class="gradient-text">Me</span>
  </h2>
  <p class="section-subtitle reveal">
    Product-minded software engineer focused on speed, reliability, and business
    impact.
  </p>

  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-image-wrapper reveal-left">
      <div class="about-image-border">
        <img
          src="/images/profile.webp"
          alt="Dhanush Kukatla — Software Engineer"
          class="about-image"
          width="400"
          height="400"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="image-decoration dec-1"></div>
      <div class="image-decoration dec-2"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-text reveal-right">
      <h3 class="about-heading">
        The Engineer You Hire When <br /><span class="gradient-text"
          >Outcomes Matter</span
        >
      </h3>
      <p class="about-paragraph">
        I am a software engineer who combines product thinking with deep
        engineering execution. I build systems that are not only technically
        sound, but also clearly tied to user and business outcomes. One example:
        an AI knowledge assistant serving 10K+ users/day with measurable
        improvements in support efficiency.
      </p>
      <p class="about-paragraph">
        My strengths include scalable backend design, cloud-native deployment,
        real-time architectures, and AI integration in production. If your team
        needs someone who can own ambiguous problems and ship dependable
        software quickly, I will add value from day one.
      </p>

      <div class="about-highlights">
        <div class="highlight glass glass-hover spotlight tilt-card">
          <span class="highlight-icon">🏗️</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Execution at Scale</strong>
            <span>Production systems from architecture through deployment</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight glass glass-hover spotlight tilt-card">
          <span class="highlight-icon">☁️</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Cloud + AI Ready</strong>
            <span
              >AWS certified, Azure certified, and AI-first implementation
              experience</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight glass glass-hover spotlight tilt-card">
          <span class="highlight-icon">🎓</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Strong Technical Foundation</strong>
            <span
              >M.S. Computer Science + hands-on delivery across startup-paced
              teams</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.3fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  /* ── Image ── */
  .about-image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .about-image-border {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      var(--accent-1),
      var(--accent-2),
      var(--accent-3)
    );
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .about-image {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 350px;
    border-radius: calc(var(--radius-xl) - 2px);
    object-fit: cover;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
  }

  .image-decoration {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .dec-1 {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    border: 2px solid var(--accent-1);
    bottom: -20px;
    right: -20px;
    opacity: 0.3;
    animation: float 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .dec-2 {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);
    top: -15px;
    left: -15px;
    opacity: 0.5;
    animation: float 5s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
  }

  /* ── Text ── */
  .about-heading {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-paragraph {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  /* ── Highlights ── */
  .about-highlights {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .highlight {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    transition: all var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .highlight-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .highlight strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
  }

  .highlight span:last-child {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .about-image {
      max-width: 280px;
    }
  }
</style>
